Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:02.90,Header,,0,0,0,,This is a Gentlemen of the Hàn free fansub.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:06.94,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,1700,5140,6380)\pos(342.857,386.286)}Mèngdé presents a blade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.12,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,360,2040,2400)\pos(118,336)}Wáng Yǔn\NStyled: Zishī
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shào heard at Bóhǎi that \NDǒng Zhuó was abusing his authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so he wrote a confidential letter to Wáng Yǔn,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,plotting to assassinate Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, please take your seats. Do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.12,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(584,365)\fade(255,0,255,0,360,1520,1520)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,are old ministers who \Nserved the Imperial Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency, why are you crying on your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}today {\pos(352,415)}is actually not my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}I only wanted to have a meeting with you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}because I feared \NDǒng Zhuó would get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}so I made this excuse, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... so that was the real intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}Dǒng Zhuó insults His Majesty, abuses his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}and endangered the nation's spirits many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}Who would have thought
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}that the empire founded by Emperor Gāozǔ,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}who defeated Qín and Chǔ,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}which shelters us as of now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,415)}would fall at the hands of Dǒng Zhuó?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé, why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All you grand ministers do is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,wail from dusk to dawn and dawn to dusk, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You think crying can kill Dǒng Zhuó?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cáo Mèngdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your ancestors too enjoyed the Hàn Empire's favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't think of serving the nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Instead you are laughing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your reason!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't laugh at anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but at you folks, for not coming up \Nwith a single plan to kill Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Although I am untalented,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing to cut off Dǒng Zhuó's head
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and hang it on the capital city's gate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to appease the realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé, what is your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come; follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū's writing in this \Nletter is very passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he is hiding far away at Bóhǎi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It is easy for him to order people to do what he dares not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get rid of Dǒng Zhuó without a single soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I heard that you have\Nthe Seven Star dagger in your possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves like the wind\N and cuts iron like hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Its blade is peerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to follow Wǔ Fú's example and kill the traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't do. Won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You must learn from the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassinating the tyrant is easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That traitor has armored\Nbodyguards wherever he goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He also has that lackey, Lǚ Bù,\N who never leaves his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your concerns are not necessarily wrong,\Nbut not necessarily right either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó is blunt yet boorish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, Wǔ Fú's assassination failed and he lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó killed him as an example to others\Nand no one else dared to try what Wǔ Fú did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But things are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,While it has failed in the past, this time it may not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, it's still difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}It goes without saying \Nthat the traitor's heart is distrustful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}But who is he distrustful of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Without a doubt it is his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:39.52,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Yào Lí was an assassin of Wú hired to kill Prince Qìngjì of Wú during the Spring and Autumn period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}In the past, Yào Lí assassinated Qìngjì.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Even 10,000 people could \Nnot match up to Qìngjì's bravery,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}yet Yào Lí was handicapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}How was he able to succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Because Qìngjì trusted Yào Lí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Right right right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}His confidant assassinated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}It is very hard to defend\N yourself against your confidant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}I have been serving Dǒng Zhuó recently,\Nand I have gained his trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}He consults me on all matters, big or small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}I have become so close with Dǒng Zhuó\N that I can enter and leave his residence freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}If I have the Seven Star dagger,\NI can wait for a chance to assassinate the bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,425)}Success is guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé, you are a devoted official.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire is very fortunate to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the gods of Heaven and Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,your servant, the Colonel\N of Valiant Cavalry; Cáo Cāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,will assassinate the evil traitor Dǒng Zhuó
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to appease the Imperial Court, the state,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the world, and the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go through fire and water, risk life and limb, and stop at nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Rú, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé, the Premier of State is in the small pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so quiet today in the Premier's mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Premier is resting at the pavilion in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The servants are having this day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to see him,\Nyou will have to find the way yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, then please have some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Salutations, Premier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.24,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,348)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1840,2240)}Dǒng Zhuó\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you late today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My horse is frail and it couldn't endure the travel. That's why I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well why didn't you tell me sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How can an officer not have a good horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and pick out a good Xīliáng horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:43.31,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,350)\fade(255,0,255,0,320,2320,2680)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled: Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and give it to Mèngdé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Premier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have shown me great kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This bastard is strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't underestimate him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Premier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please rest, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your servant Cáo offers you\Nthe Seven Star dagger, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fine blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A fine blade indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. Come. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see which horse Fèngxiān chose for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it is a good horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful for this fine horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse is quite spirited;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, I think Cáo Cāo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,was trying to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my doubts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Premier is in the pavilion.\NYou may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,351)\fade(255,0,255,0,360,1360,1760)}Lǐ Rú
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that when you caught him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he pretended to present the blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Premier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo has no family within \Nthe capital and lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can send someone to summon him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and if he shows up,\Nthen he meant to present the blade to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does not,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then he meant to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Send someone to summon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Premier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo really wanted to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo never returned home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He rode his horse to the east gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,told the guard there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that he was sent by the \NPremier on urgent business,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and rode out of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I valued him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but he meant to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Premier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there might be accomplices to this plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Accomplices?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest this traitor. Find his accomplices!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister, we should quickly distribute\Nwanted posters to arrest the traitor Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit straight. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, isn't that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you arresting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm just a merchant passing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My surname is Huángfǔ. Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:49.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(597,360)\fade(255,0,255,0,360,2200,2560)}Chén Gōng\NStyled: Gōngtái
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:18.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,To hand him over and be rewarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:21.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,or to let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:26.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If I hand him over to Dǒng\N Zhuó the realm will curse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If I release him, my career will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You do somewhat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,bear a resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct, but there are many\N people who resemble each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a mistake by arresting me, and I don't blame you.\NJust hurry and let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, imprison him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.88,0:24:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.50,0:24:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.47,0:24:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My surname is Huángfǔ.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.25,0:24:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must you hide your identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.37,0:24:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to Luòyáng to seek\N a government post in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.20,0:24:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to meet you, Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.13,0:25:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Premier treated you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you invite trouble for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.53,0:25:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}A sparrow cannot understand the aspirations of a swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.21,0:25:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}You compare yourself to a swan, \Nbut how can you know the others are sparrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop blabbering!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now that you've caught me, hand me over and claim your prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.72,0:25:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.01,0:25:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasures and a title of a marquis.\N Is that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.70,0:25:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot for a small magistrate like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.35,0:25:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.12,0:26:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming a marquis is something\NI never would have dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.91,0:26:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have sent you to the capital today and be rewarded for my service.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.11,0:26:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But then why
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.57,0:26:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,did I imprison you for now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.50,0:26:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and not reveal your identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.99,0:26:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're going to release me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.36,0:26:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure I will release you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.96,0:26:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you going to do to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.64,0:26:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.54,0:26:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Premier trusted you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.34,0:26:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but you attempted to assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.26,0:26:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the reason for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.04,0:27:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}For generations, my family was favored by the Hàn Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.89,0:27:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}If I turned from my country,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.48,0:27:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}how would I differ from a beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.68,0:27:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}That's why I bowed down to Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.23,0:27:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}It was to find a chance to kill the bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.00,0:27:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Yet now I would fail and my efforts are for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.20,0:27:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}But alas, perhaps this is the will of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.52,0:27:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Then, where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.29,0:27:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}I will return to my hometown and issue an edict
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}calling all the lords of the\Nrealm to march against Dǒng Zhuó!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.79,0:27:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}An expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Against Dǒng Zhuó in support of the Hàn!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.77,0:27:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit, accept my respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.40,0:28:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your prisoner does not dare\N to accept such a virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.96,0:28:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.92,0:28:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not sit first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.52,0:28:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where your hometown is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.29,0:28:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My father and his family are \Nall live in Dōng commandery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.84,0:28:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and children also reside in Dōng commandery!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.48,0:28:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you and I are fellow townsmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.79,0:28:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.91,0:28:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My surname is Chén and my\N forename is Gōng, styled Gōngtái.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.93,0:28:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After you return home,\Nhow are you going to rally the lords of the realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.20,0:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}Now, the realm is in chaos and all the lords are beginning to rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.84,0:28:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}After I return home,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.24,0:29:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}I will use all my family's wealth to conscript an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.94,0:29:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}I am good friends with Yuán Shào, \Nstyled Běnchū, of Jìzhōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.88,0:29:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}His family has served the \Nnation for many generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.98,0:29:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}He has deep connections\N with the nobles of the realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.14,0:29:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}so I can cooperate with him to call an expedition against Dǒng Zhuó and save the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.61,0:29:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}I am sure they will respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.04,0:29:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.46,0:29:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}Dǒng Zhuó runs amok and is\N a calamity for the state and the people;
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.71,0:29:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}the whole realm wants to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.56,0:30:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}You're following the will of heaven and the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.38,0:30:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}You will surely succeed in your undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.11,0:30:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,420)}However, at the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I would have\N handed you over for a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.16,0:30:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Chén Gōng, am not just a petty official,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.54,0:30:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never met a worthy master.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.05,0:30:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply moved by your loyalty \Ntowards the nation and the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.08,0:30:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will relinquish my duty as county magistrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.53,0:30:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and follow you to help in this great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.43,0:31:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.24,0:31:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a person named Lǚ Bóshē lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.18,0:31:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my father's sworn brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.59,0:31:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the night, why don't we stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.53,0:31:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can ask about my family's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.15,0:31:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't reject his sworn brother's own son, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.87,0:31:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.69,0:31:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.52,0:31:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your master in?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.61,0:31:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.15,0:31:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, there's someone here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.40,0:31:50.24,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554,191)\fade(255,0,255,0,360,1520,1840)}Lǚ Bóshē
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.49,0:31:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.02,0:31:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.78,0:31:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Āmán.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.78,0:31:56.34,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: Āmán is Cáo Cāo's childhood name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.01,0:31:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Āmán!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.79,0:32:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.66,0:32:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.45,0:32:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Come in quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.72,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.30,0:32:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.47,0:32:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit, Gōngtái.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.70,0:32:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Āmán,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.81,0:32:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.84,0:32:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Imperial Court was looking everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.05,0:32:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.81,0:32:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.80,0:32:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.60,0:32:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father has already taken refuge at Chénliú.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.23,0:33:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to assassinate Dǒng Zhuó,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.90,0:33:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so I fled the capital city in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.51,0:33:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran until I was arrested at Zhōngmóu county.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.80,0:33:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Were it not for magistrate Chén\Nsacrificing his post to escape with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.24,0:33:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your nephew would have long been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.81,0:33:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Were it not for you, the entire Cáo clan would have ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.22,0:33:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat and rest here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.77,0:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.44,0:33:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, take a rest. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.45,0:33:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:33:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.85,0:34:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have good wine at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.19,0:34:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the village and purchase some for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.74,0:34:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sleep here in peace tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.78,0:34:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.02,0:34:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.71,0:34:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. What is that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bóshē is not a close relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.43,0:35:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He left in a hurry and has yet to come back. It's too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.53,0:35:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharpen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.92,0:35:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to that. If we don't act now, we'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.62,0:35:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.06,0:35:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.48,0:36:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.18,0:36:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle wanted to slaughter a pig to treat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.10,0:36:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They died for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.36,0:36:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.71,0:36:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.88,0:37:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So Uncle really did buy wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.97,0:37:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, why are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.33,0:37:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As a criminal, I would not dare to stay for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.19,0:37:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, please wait! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.22,0:37:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told my family to\N slaughter a pig for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, why not rest at \Nmy humble house for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.76,0:37:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.09,0:37:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.91,0:37:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nephew, what's that on your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.99,0:37:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.68,0:37:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,look who's behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.41,0:38:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time, you killed by accident. What did you kill him for now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.20,0:38:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If Bóshē came back home, he would have seen his entire family murdered. Would he let that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.80,0:38:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He would lead men to pursue us
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.69,0:38:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and we would be doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.22,0:38:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.65,0:38:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.63,0:38:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.31,0:38:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying won't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.07,0:38:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.33,0:38:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You murdered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.36,0:38:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.81,0:38:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.14,0:39:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}Rather I {\pos(352,430)}betray the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.25,0:39:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,430)}than let the world betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now I followed him for the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.22,0:39:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, I can't kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.16,0:39:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't stand with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.31,0:39:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will leave now. You may go ahead with your 'great cause'
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.86,0:40:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo went back to Chénliú afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.45,0:40:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He spent all his family's wealth to recruit an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.88,0:40:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He contacted Yuán Shào and sent out declarations to all provinces to march against Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.52,0:40:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They were answered all across the realm.
